{"tid":1390159,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚惠珠針對連登指要網管 倡訂「反蒙面法」被斥違人權","createTime":"2019-07-31T05:35:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T05:57:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3ba8b8680575217af3dd638aab583f378467b413","tid":1390159,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:35:19.000Z","msg":"建制派為阻止民間的抗爭運動，接連拋出不同修例及立法建議，例如民建聯倡議提高港鐵罰則以阻嚇於車廂發動的不合作運動，身兼基本法委員會副主任的譚惠珠今早更在電台節目指，今次修例風波除要透過施政解決社會對民生不滿，更要以法律途徑重整社會秩序，例如考慮訂立「反蒙面法」，甚或管制網絡上引人犯罪的消息，矛盾指向今次反修例中動員力極強的連登，她警告不能低估網絡對年輕人的影響，「網絡方面，危及別人安全或社會秩序嘅信息係咪可以考慮過濾一下？」有民主派斥譚的建議不治標也不治本。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190731/59880971\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190731%2F59880971&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qneCCrfoqRshWq79J%2FX5JLMA%3D&h=79dbfabf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190731%2F59880971&h=c41a0a52\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190731/59880971</a>"},{"pid":"de939d460c781eeb994d1fb827fb29ca8ecad1f4","tid":1390159,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:44:52.000Z","msg":"相由心生"},{"pid":"3ad4cc3368609381cb45b9a10145e3628571f64a","tid":1390159,"uid":261937,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:45:59.000Z","msg":"要通知伊斯蘭世界"},{"pid":"0621c7f465ed62ecbf5e8df4204f2fc7026ec841","tid":1390159,"uid":97949,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:48:11.000Z","msg":"警賊都通用？"},{"pid":"9459dd929780705be3887aad29011a99d692e4df","tid":1390159,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0621c7f465ed62ecbf5e8df4204f2fc7026ec841","tid":1390159,"uid":97949,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:48:11.000Z","msg":"警賊都通用？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:49:22.